"title": "4687: snake",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4687",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A reptile, often associated with cunning and danger, or occasionally with satanic temptation.</p>\n<h2>Snakes as crawling reptiles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:14\">GEN 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:25\">ISA 65:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:17\">MIC 7:17</a></p>\n<h2>Snakes are dangerous</h2>\n<h3>Both to animals and human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:17\">GEN 49:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:3\">EXO 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:9-Exod7:13\">EXO 7:9–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:32\">PRO 23:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:8\">ECC 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:11\">ECC 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:6\">ISA 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:3-Acts28:6\">ACT 28:3–28:6</a></p>\n<h3>Some are poisonous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:29\">ISA 14:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:15\">DEU 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:33\">DEU 32:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:14\">JOB 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:16\">JOB 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:19\">REV 9:19</a></p>\n<h3>They were sometimes used to bring God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:9\">1CO 10:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:4-Num21:6\">NUM 21:4–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:19\">AMO 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:3\">AMO 9:3</a></p>\n<h3>They may be overcome</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:13\">PSA 91:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:18\">MRK 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:19\">LUK 10:19</a></p>\n<h3>One day they will be rendered harmless</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:8\">ISA 11:8</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Snakes used symbolically</h2>\n<h3>Of Israel's enemies</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:1\">ISA 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:22\">JER 46:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:34\">JER 51:34</a></p>\n<h3>Of cunning and intelligence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:16\">MAT 10:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Of something harmful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:9-Matt7:10\">MAT 7:9–7:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:11\">LUK 11:11</a></p>\n<h3>Of the ungodly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:4-Ps58:5\">PSA 58:4–58:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:3\">PSA 140:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:7\">MAT 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:34\">MAT 12:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:33\">MAT 23:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:13\">ROM 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Of Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:13\">GEN 3:1–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:2\">REV 20:2</a></p>\n<h3>Of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:15\">JHN 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:7-Num21:9\">NUM 21:7–21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a></p>",
